      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.sobLlAGQkmWcFBFx]{Magic Hack}</p>\n<p>As a full action, you can transform your body into a technological construct for a number of rounds equal to your Intelligence modifier. In this state, you gain immunity to @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.v9RNVTqyTyaPchvd]{Bleed}, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.JaRMioj4isNp7r1P.JournalEntryPage.gBhZDjh30JEyh7DY]{Disease}, nonlethal damage, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.NV4qXRDgb7zTNkW2]{Paralysis}, @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.JaRMioj4isNp7r1P.JournalEntryPage.ZaS9H4rwaFIQTUBC]{Poison}, and @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.CvsDp0GvojxiF2jz]{Stunning}. You gain a +4 enhancement bonus to Fortitude saving throws, unless the effect prompting the saving throw works on technological constructs. You can end the transformation early with a swift action. You canâ€™t use this ability again until you spend 1 Resolve Point to regain Stamina Points after a 10-minute rest.</p>\n<p><em>Immunities must be manually added by the GM / player.</em></p>"
